==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[inhibere]], [[inhibit-]]'', "to hold in", "to check", "to restrain", from ''[[in-#Latin|in-]]'', + ''[[habere]]'', "to have", "to hold".
===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|inhibit||}}
# to [[hinder]]; to [[restrain]]
